fail creating allow the path:  /etc/nginx/sites-enabled







to work with multuple web-server:

in config to write in file:

/etc/nginx/nginx.conf

to section HTTP write:

upstream name_upstraem {
        
        server 127.0.0.1:number_port1(8000);
        server 127.0.0.1:number_port2(8001);
        server 127.0.0.1:number_port3(8002);
}

location / {

         proxy_pass http://name_upstraem
}

